codes.biscuit.skyblocklib.model

Class SkyblockItemAbility

  • java.lang.Object
    • codes.biscuit.skyblocklib.model.SkyblockItemAbility

  • public final class SkyblockItemAbility
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Skyblock Item ability. This class is meant to only represent values provided from the item-abilities.json file and is thus immutable.

        name - Non-null and non-empty ability name
        cooldownSeconds - Cooldown in positive or 0 seconds

        itemId - Non-null and non-empty Skyblock Item ID
        otherItems - Nullable list of other Item IDs that have this ability
